    <h2>The Solution</h2>
    <p><strong>GoProBono</strong> connects law students and attorneys with real legal issues from underserved communities. We streamline supervision, hour tracking, and documentation—making the 50-hour bar requirement easier and more impactful.</p>
  </section>

